content: I was thinking of exploring more abstract expressionist artists, but I'm also curious about other art movements. I recently saw some amazing ancient Egyptian artifacts at the Metropolitan Museum of Art, and I was blown away by the grandeur of the golden mask of Pharaoh Tutankhamun. I took some photos to remember the details, and I'd love to learn more about other art movements and styles. Can you recommend any notable artists or styles that I might find interesting?
